node.text:
"If you don’t chase your dreams, who else is gonna do it?” asked  multisport badass KC Deane during a recent Summer Anthem trip in Jackson Hole. And we all know it’s not a true Teton session without sampling the goods. From pulling rock with @griffpost, to flowing hard with dirt-savant @rowdyflow, to chatting the meaning of life with legendary JH rancher, Grant Golligher, Deane played hard with some of the raddest locals in town. 

Whether getting muddy—or gettin’ sendy—Deane dials it in with TGR Supply. That way, he’s ready for anything: from leisure shenanigans, to Type-II sufferfest, to trying to go as big as @kaijonesski off the lip. For more of Deane’s Summer Anthem exploits, stay tuned and see what gear you should be rocking to look good and feel good in the mountains!

node.title: TGR Presents KC Deane & The Locals

node.text:
"If you don’t chase your dreams, who else is gonna do it?” asked  multisport badass KC Deane during a recent Summer Anthem trip in Jackson Hole. And we all know it’s not a true Teton session without sampling the goods. From pulling rock with @griffpost, to flowing hard with dirt-savant @rowdyflow, to chatting the meaning of life with legendary JH rancher, Grant Golligher, Deane played hard with some of the raddest locals in town. 

Whether getting muddy—or gettin’ sendy—Deane dials it in with TGR Supply. That way, he’s ready for anything: from leisure shenanigans, to Type-II sufferfest, to trying to go as big as @kaijonesski off the lip. For more of Deane’s Summer Anthem exploits, stay tuned and see what gear you should be rocking to look good and feel good in the mountains!
